name: CakeWalk
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cake walk
Developer Terms of Use
des: Alexa asks for the user's birthday and will ask again for missing info until the system has the day, month and year of the user's birthday. Alexa will remember the birthday and each time the skill is opened it will tell the user how long it is until their next birthday or wish them a happy birthday if their birthday is the day the skill is opened.
